    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The thorn draws blood for the hungry rose. Make an attack. If it hits, it deals an additional 1d6 damage. You may heal yourself and allies within Close range of the struck creature for a number of hit points equal to 2d6 + your initiation modifier, divided as you choose between you and your allies. If the target is sprouted, this maneuver heals an additional d6 per sprout stack the target has, to a maximum of 5d6.</p>"
